Flood & Learn basic config:
conf t
    install feature-set fabric
    nv overlay
    feature nv overlay
    feature pim
    feature vn-segment-vlan-based
    !
    vlan 11
        vn-segment 11111
    !
    interface loopback0
    no shut
    ip add 1.1.1.51/32
    igmp join 224.11.11.11
    !
    PIM BIDIR config
    !
    interface nve1
        no shutdown
        source-interface loopback0
        member vni 11111
            mcast-group 224.11.11.11


BGP EVPN basic config:
conf t
    install feature-set fabric
    nv overlay
    feature nv overlay
    feature pim
    feature bgp
    feature vn-segment-vlan-based
    !
    vlan 11
        vn-segment 11111
    !
    interface loopback0
    no shut
    ip add 1.1.1.51/32
    igmp join 224.11.11.11
    !
    PIM BIDIR config
    !
    interface nve1
        no shutdown
        source-interface loopback0
        host-reachability protocol bgp
        member vni 11111
            mcast-group 224.11.11.11
    !
    router bgp 12345
        neighbor 1.1.1.71
            remote-as 12345
            update-source loopback0
            address-family l2vpn evpn
                send-community both
         neighbor 1.1.1.72
            remote-as 12345
            update-source loopback0
            address-family l2vpn evpn
                send-community both       
    !
    evpn
        vni 11111 l2
            rd auto
            route-target import auto
            route-target export auto
    
